title: Martin Boszorád
text:
Martin Boszorád (born 13 November 1989) is a <a href="Slovakia">Slovak</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> defender who currently plays for ASV Nickelsdorf in <a href="Austria">Austria</a>.
Ex-Clubs.
Nitra U19 (2008/2009)
<a href="FC%20Nitra">FC Nitra</a> (2014/2015)
Ruzomberok (2016/2017)
Zlate Moravce (2017/2018)
<a href="Gy%C5%91ri%20ETO%20FC">ETO FC Győr</a> (2017/2018)
